Added a Nautobot UI ViewSet implementation for Django admin LogEntry under the Users app.
- Added LogEntry proxy model to support Nautobot UI rendering.
- Implemented LogEntry UI list and detail views using NautobotUIViewSet and the UI Component Framework.
- Added LogEntry navigation under the Administration → Authentication tab.
- Added LogEntry filtering, search, and table rendering with action flag badge styling.
- Enabled detail view provenance support via created and last_updated aliases.